Package com.example.cardiacrecord

Class MeasurementData

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.cardiacrecord.MeasurementData
  • public class MeasurementData
extends java.lang.Object
    The MeasurementData class represents a collection of UserRVModal measurements. It provides methods to add, delete, edit, and retrieve measurements.
